snippet.title: Ten Thousand Coins - 2nd Trailer (Turn-Based RPG)
snippet.description:
Ten Thousand Coins on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1157900/Ten_Thousand_Coins_The_Golden_Merchant/

Ten Thousand Coins: The Golden Merchant is a story-driven merchant adventure about a bold merchant fox girl who gets into big debt trouble against the mighty Basilisk Company. She soon finds herself in the midst of chaos and must trade, earn coins, and make tough decisions in order to pay back a colossal 10,000 gold coins.

#trailer #indiegames #gaming
